Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.38,0:00:45.36,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yea Yea Yea
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.36,0:00:48.41,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The Rock City Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.81,0:00:52.61,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Oh baby 跳吧 跳吧 跳越牆壁 With my guitar
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.61,0:00:55.26,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}直到傳達到為止 oh yeah 唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.26,0:00:57.97,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Just music 僅僅只是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.97,0:01:00.75,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}奉獻給你喔 oh yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.75,0:01:04.37,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}真的有很多相同點嗎? With my guitar
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.37,0:01:07.38,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}邊探索 Yea 邊唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.38,0:01:10.13,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Just love 僅僅只是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.13,0:01:12.71,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}追趕上 be free!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.71,0:01:16.31,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}My 完美夢想
