Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.04,0:01:34.26,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}把夢作為同伴哦 Yea
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.26,0:01:35.84,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I wanna believe the singing on beat
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.84,0:01:37.53,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\be1}most recently is like recess for me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.53,0:01:38.78,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\be1}pretty pretty please,no birds and the bees
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.78,0:01:40.52,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\be1}but ecstasy with extra cheese
